_for_Google_Ads\" >3. Key Metrics to Monitor in GA4 for Google Ads<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-76\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#4_Audience_Creation_with_GA4\" >4. Audience Creation with GA4<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-77\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#How_to_audit_and_optimise_campaigns_weekly\" >How to audit and optimise campaigns weekly<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-78\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#1_Check_Budget_Utilisation_and_Pacing\" >1. Check Budget Utilisation and Pacing<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-79\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#2_Review_the_Search_Terms_Report\" >2. Review the Search Terms Report<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-80\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#3_Analyse_Keyword_and_Match_Type_Performance\" >3. Analyse Keyword and Match Type Performance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-81\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/google-advertising\/the-ultimate-guide-to-google-ads-in-kenya-how-to-get-real-roi-in-2025\/#4_Inspect_Ad_Performance\" >4. Inspect Ad Performance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-t